  "dateViewedByCreator": null,
  "desc": "EA SPORTS FC 26 version 1.5.1 will soon be available for all platforms, and it will include:\n\n**Ultimate Team**\n\nAddressed the following issues: \n\n- When adding or swapping Player Items to a Squad or SBC, the filter was using Any by default instead of selecting the position highlighted.\n\n‌\n\n**Career Mode**\n\nMade the following changes:\n\n- Updated some social media posts.\n- Updated the injury duration selection in the Injuries and Suspensions menu.\n- Improved visibility of qualification zones in competition standings in Deeper Sim. \n\n‌\n\nAddressed the following issues:\n\n- Swapping to the Position tab while in Development Plans would cause Role Growth to disappear.\n- Addressed instances of overlapping text.\n- When playing matches in Manager Live, all players on the field were using the same boots.\n- In certain challenges, some leagues were shown as unavailable when attempting to replace teams. \n- Some players were incorrectly displayed as out of position in the match preview screen.\n- Sometimes, Scout reports could provide incorrect attribute values.\n\n‌\n\n**Clubs**\n\nAddressed the following issues: \n\n- Further adjusted Match Rating calculation logic for CAMs to avoid unintentionally high calculations.\n\n‌\n\n**General, Audio, and Visual**\n\nMade the following changes:\n\n- Updated some crests, banners, scarves, flags, scenes, camera angles, overlays, celebrations, text, hair, ad boards and cinematics.\n\nAddressed the following issues:\n\n- Addressed various stability issues that could have occurred.\n\n‌\n\nWant to provide us direct feedback about EA SPORTS FC 26? [https://go.ea.com/fc26pfp](https://go.ea.com/fc26pfp \"‌\") and let us know what you think, it only takes a few minutes.\n\nThanks to those who’ve provided and continue to provide feedback. Throughout the course of the EA SPORTS FC 26 season, we'll provide you with more information and updates if and when they become available. Be sure to follow \\@‌EASFCDIRECT on X as well as WhatsApp, and check out the EA SPORTS FC Tracker for the latest news and updates.",
